# Worker and RabbitMQ

- Redis is not the queue — jobs go through RabbitMQ
- Manual ack only after DB reflects terminal job state (or safe retry path)
- Max 5 jobs in flight; max 3 attempts on transient failures with backoff + jitter
- Permanent failures → DLQ with reason; update batch job row accordingly
- Idempotent processing: duplicate delivery must not double-count batch success/failure
- SIGTERM: stop consuming, finish or requeue in-flight, no lost messages
